* Springs (March to May): Mild and pleasant, with average highs around 18°C (64°F) and lows around 8°C (46°F). It's a great time to see the city come alive with blooming flowers and greenery.
* Summers (June to August): Mild and occasionally warm, with average highs around 23°C (73°F) and lows around 14°C (57°F). However, it's not unusual to experience some cooler days, especially in the mornings and evenings.
* Autumns (September to November): Cool and sometimes rainy, with average highs around 15°C (59°F) and lows around 8°C (46°F). The leaves changing colors can make for a lovely backdrop, though.
